104
00:12:11,760 --> 00:12:13,280
Think about it and choose wisely, Tharn.

105
00:12:30,520 --> 00:12:32,160
Who are you looking for?

106
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:35,040
Oh, just my friend.

107
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,920
Hmm, a friend?

108
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:44,320
Oh, is that Wi? We’re here!

109
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:50,760
I haven’t seen you for ages. I thought you already disappeared.

110
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:55,880
- Good evening, Grandma.
- Good evening.
How are you doing?

111
00:12:55,920 --> 00:13:00,320
I’m doing well. I haven’t seen you for so long. You hardly come visit me.

112
00:13:00,640 --> 00:13:03,920
I just open my art gallery so I’m a little busy.

113
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:08,560
Hello, Phaya.
Hello.

114
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:10,440
And this is...

115
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:15,680
Oh, her name is Dujdao. She’s my junior friend when I studied in France.

116
00:13:16,680 --> 00:13:21,520
Hello, I’m Dao. You must be Wi. He often told me about you.

117
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:23,520
Really? What did he tell you?

118
00:13:24,400 --> 00:13:26,160
She’s my friend too.

119
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:29,880
You can ask me if you want to know anything about her.
I know a lot more than he does.

120
00:13:29,880 --> 00:13:31,320
I’ll tell you later then.

121
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:36,960
